---
// src/components/Navbar.astro
// Estructura original 100% intacta de Jose Luis - Paleta Dark Tech Premium
---

<nav class="nav">
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <img src="/images/tienda.png" alt="foto" class="img-circular" />
  <h1 class="titulo">artezanias killa</h1>

  <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css"
  />

  <h3 class="subtitulo">
    Descubre la magia de los andes. Ropa de alpaca, carteras de cuero y <br />
    accesorios hechos a mano por artesanos peruanos, esto esta desarrollado por jose
    luis_xd, sin criticar por fis :).
  </h3>

  <button class="btn-catalogo" onclick="window.location.href='/catalogo'">
    Ver catalogo
  </button>

  <button class="btn-whatsapp" onclick="window.location.href='/contacto'">
    consultar
  </button>

  <div class="redes">
    <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank">
      <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i>
    </a>

    <a href="https://tiktok.com" target="_blank">
      <i class="fa-brands fa-tiktok"></i>
    </a>
  </div>

  <h3 class="pregunta">¿Que estas buscando?</h3>

  <h4 class="explora">Explora nuestros catalogos principales</h4>

  <div class="contenedor">
    <div class="card">
      <img src="/images/ropa_alpaca.png" alt="producto 1" />
      <h3>ropa de alpaca</h3>
      <a href="/catalogo" class="btn-catalogo">
        <span class="flecha"></span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="/images/cartera_cuero.png" alt="producto 2" />
      <h3>carteras y cuero</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <img src="/images/accesorios.png" alt="producto 3" />
      <h3>accesorios</h3>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<style>
  < > * {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .nav {
    background:
      radial-gradient(
        circle at top right,
        rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15),
        transparent 30%
      ),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #020617, #0f172a, #1e293b);

    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;

    margin: 1rem;

    border-radius: 30px;

    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);

    box-shadow: 0 25px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);

    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .img-circular {
    width: 160px;
    height: 160px;

    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;

    border: 4px solid #38bdf8;

    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 12px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.08),
      0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);

    transition: 0.4s;
  }

  .img-circular:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .titulo {
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4.8rem);

    font-weight: 900;

    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;

    letter-spacing: -2px;

    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffffff, #cbd5e1, #38bdf8);

    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .subtitulo {
    color: #94a3b8;

    font-size: 1rem;

    line-height: 1.8;

    max-width: 850px;

    margin: 0 auto 2rem auto;
  }

  .btn-catalogo,
  .btn-whatsapp {
    border: none;

    padding: 15px 30px;

    border-radius: 999px;

    font-size: 0.95rem;

    font-weight: 700;

    cursor: pointer;

    margin: 0.5rem;

    transition: 0.3s;
  }

  .btn-catalogo {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #2563eb);

    color: white;

    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.35);
  }

  .btn-catalogo:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);

    box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.45);
  }

  .btn-whatsapp {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);

    color: white;

    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);

    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .btn-whatsapp:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);

    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
  }

  .redes {
    display: flex;

    justify-content: center;

    gap: 1.5rem;

    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .redes a {
    width: 55px;
    height: 55px;

    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;

    border-radius: 50%;

    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);

    color: white;

    font-size: 1.4rem;

    transition: 0.3s;
  }

  .redes a:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);

    background: #38bdf8;

    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.4);
  }

  .pregunta {
    color: white;

    font-size: 2.3rem;

    font-weight: 800;

    margin-top: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .explora {
    color: #94a3b8;

    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contenedor {
    display: flex;

    justify-content: center;

    gap: 2rem;

    flex-wrap: wrap;

    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .card {
    width: 250px;

    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);

    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);

    border-radius: 22px;

    overflow: hidden;

    transition: 0.35s;

    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);

    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.03);

    border-color: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.4);

    box-shadow: 0 25px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .card img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 180px;

    object-fit: cover;

    transition: 0.4s;
  }

  .card:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.08);
  }

  .card h3 {
    color: white;

    padding: 1rem;

    font-size: 1rem;

    text-transform: uppercase;

    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .card .btn-catalogo {
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;

    padding: 0;

    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;

    margin: 0 auto 1rem auto;

    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .flecha {
    border: solid white;

    border-width: 0 2px 2px 0;

    display: inline-block;

    padding: 3px;

    transform: rotate(-45deg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .titulo {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    .pregunta {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }

    .contenedor {
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .card {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 320px;
    }
  }
</style>
